  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Line a baking sheet with parchment paper.",
    "Place the sea bass fillets on the baking sheet.",
    "Drizzle with coconut oil, sprinkle with smoked paprika, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bake for 8-10 minutes or until the sea bass is cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, warm the pandan leaf wraps by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Once the sea bass is cooked, flake it into small pieces and place it onto the warmed pandan leaf wraps.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with chopped cilantro if desired."
